  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0da9\u0dd4 \u0db6\u0ddc\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d9a\u0dca\u0d9a\u0dcf \u0db1\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd3 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Sister sells drugs to drink",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minuwangoda police said that a sister who sold her fifteen-year-old sister to a heroin smuggler for 15000 rupees and 01 heroin was arrested.",
        "The heroin smuggler who took the girl with money and heroin was also arrested with 5120 mg of heroin.",
        "The police also say that the sister who sold the girl is addicted to heroin.",
        "It has been revealed from the police investigation that the girl was taken care of by this person after the mother was imprisoned.",
        "Based on information received that the suspect residing in West Nilpanagoda was involved in heroin trafficking, the suspect's house was raided and the suspect was arrested with 5120 mg of heroin. There, the police officers have asked who is this little girl in the house of the suspect.",
        "The suspect's mother, who was in the house at that time, disclosed the incident and took the girl into police custody and arrested the suspect's sister, who allegedly sold the girl, police said."
      ],
